                        <div class="mb-3 border-bottom pb-3">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                                <img width="40" src="/images/default_profile.svg" class="rounded-circle me-2" alt="User">
                                <strong>John Doe</strong>
                                <small class="text-muted ms-auto">2 hours ago</small>
                            </div>
                            <p class="mb-2">Just launched my new project! So excited to share it with everyone. #coding #webdev</p>
